column1: If numeric gdcb greater than or equal to 2 OR ( categorical fxbp equal to no AND numeric ufem greater than 59 ) , then it is occasionally speff.
If categorical xiux equal to yes , then it is typically tupa.
If categorical xiux equal to no AND ( numeric gdcb greater than or equal to 2 OR numeric ufem lesser than or equal to 27 ) , then it is always tulver.
